T16TD4438E:299a-0: @299a * // mtshon 'og 'byung ba rlung gi sa rlung gi gnas so//
T16TD4438E:299a-6: rlung mkhris pa bad kan rlung sprul dzum /
T16TD4438E:299a-8: shig srin bu padma can khrag p'a ni /
T16TD4438E:299a-11: chu nya rta rkan 'og 'byung ba me'i sa mkhris pa'i gnas so//
T16TD4438E:299a-16: mkhris pa rlung bad kan mkhris pa la ba ka / ba ai sa /
T16TD4438E:299a-18: sreg pa bya rog sbal pa rakta /
T16TD4438E:299a-21: re ba khrag chu byi'u rta chag gi 'og 'byung ba chu'i sa bad kan gyi gnas so//
T16TD4438E:299a-27: bad kan ham sa r'a dza /
T16TD4438E:299a-31: ngang pa'i rgyal po rma bya chu khrag p'a ni /
T16TD4438E:299a-34: chu phug ron khyim bya ` zas dang spyod lam bstan pa ni /
T16TD4438E:299a-35: rlung gi nad mtha' dag la /
T16TD4438E:299a-36: dro sar dal bar 'dug / me la sro zhing byug pa byed /
T16TD4438E:299a-38: sha dang de'i khu ba gtong /
T16TD4438E:299a-39: mkhris pa'i nad la b'a la dang shri khanda gnyis zhib bar btags la chur sbyar ba'i byug pa byed /
T16TD4438E:299a-41: nad tshabs che na lto bkag gtong /
T16TD4438E:299a-42: gzhan pag thug kho na bsten no //
T16TD4438E:299a-43: bad kan la grang dro ran par byas la dal bus 'chag / sran rtsam sogs zas yang zhing 'ju ba'i rigs bsten /
T16TD4438E:299a-44: bcud can dang lci ba'i rigs 'dzem mo //
T16TD4438E:299a-46: rdo gzhong gi nang du dngul chu zho nyi shu rtsa bzhi blug / de dang rdza rnying pa'am so phag khyor gang tsam dang mnyam du nyin gnyis kyi bar du nyed /
T16TD4438E:299a-47: de nas chu gtsang mar bsrings te dngul chu dang sa rang sar phye /
T16TD4438E:299b-0: chu khog ma phyed tsam blug de la 'bras bu gsum dang rgya gar stod ja zhib par btags pa khyor gang tsam zhig blug / gong gi dngul chu ras gtsang mas dril la skud pas kha bsdams te @299b chur sor bzhi tsam ma reg par khebs gcod la btags te kha legs par bsgrigs nas rlangs pa mi 'chor ba byed /
T16TD4438E:299b-1: nyi ma'i bzhi cha gcig tsam me btang la rlangs pas btsos /
T16TD4438E:299b-2: chu grang thag chod pa dang bton te rdo gzhong legs par bkrus pa'i nang du blugs la shing ghi wa kva ra'i shing gzhogs dang mnyam du nyin gsum gyi bar grib ma la brdung ba dang nyi ma la bsro ba chu tshod re tsam gyi bar re mos su byed /
T16TD4438E:299b-3: de nas shing che la chang gar mas khu ba byas nas nyin gsum gyi bar la nyed cing /
T16TD4438E:299b-4: 'di nas gzung nyin re re nyi mar 'jog thengs gnyis tsam las sngon ma lugs kyi re mos mi dgos /
T16TD4438E:299b-5: de nas skyes pa'i chu dang ra'i 'o ma /
T16TD4438E:299b-7: ba sar pa'i chu rnams dang mnyam du rim pa bzhin nyin gsum re nyed /
T16TD4438E:299b-8: de nas nyi ma me tog gi lo ma logs su brdungs pa'i khu ba /
T16TD4438E:299b-9: sgog skya rdzogs pa'i khu ba /
T16TD4438E:299b-10: ba sar ba'i chu rnams dang mnyam du go rim bzhin nyin re nyed /
T16TD4438E:299b-11: de nas mu zi ser po zho nyi shu rtsa bzhi zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:299b-12: lcags snod du ba mar sar pa bskol ba'i btsag chod pa dang btab la me cung zad btang nas ba'i 'o ma'i nang du dal bus blug la snyigs ma ma shor ba byed cing /
T16TD4438E:299b-14: mar dang 'o ma gnyis 'dres nas mu zi gting du 'khur ba ltar chags yong pa de dang gong gi dngul chu gnyis bsres nas cung zad nyed /
T16TD4438E:299b-15: rdo gzhong zhig tu su ma la zho phyed bzhir ra'i 'o ma cung zad re blug nas nyed /
T16TD4438E:299b-16: yang skam pa dang ldugs pa sogs nyin gsum gyi bar byed /
T16TD4438E:299b-17: ba sar pa'i chu dang 'o ma so sor rim bzhin nyid gsum re'i bar gong bzhin skam 'thag byas la tshar ba dang gong gi dngul chu dang mu zi'i zla la bsres /
T16TD4438E:299b-18: rdo gzhong nang du rgya tsha zho do skyes pa'i chu dang mnyam du skam 'thag gong bzhin nyin gsum gyi bar byas nas dngul chu'i zla la bsres pa de rnams rdo gzhong gi nang du nyin bdun gyi bar du skam nyed byed /
T16TD4438E:300a-1: shel gyi dam pe ras kyis dril la 'jim pa byugs /
T16TD4438E:300a-2: de skams pa dang yang ras dang 'jim pa rim pa bdun gyi bar dril ba'i nang du gsum gnyis tsam gang ba blug / lcags kyi skya ba dam per bcug / rdza'i khog ma gting du bye ma sor gsum tsam gting pa'i steng du bzhag ste kha 'tshams par bye mas stems /
T16TD4438E:300a-3: dam pe'i nang du zha nye zho phyed do blug ste /
T16TD4438E:300a-4: lcags mdas dal bus dkrugs pa dang nyi shar nas nyi ma rgas tsam gyi bar me gtong /
T16TD4438E:300a-5: de nas lcags mda' bton la kha rgya tsha btags pa'i chus brdzis pa'i 'dam gyis bcad /
T16TD4438E:300a-6: de steng bye ma bkab ste khebs rgyab la nyin zhag phrug gcig gi par me shin tu tsha ba mtshams ma chad par btang /
T16TD4438E:300a-7: de nas bye ma grang thag ma chod ring tho ma btang bar bzhag / grang nges pa dang bton la dal bus dam pe bcag la phyung bas dngul chu dug bral lhad med du yod do /
T16TD4438E:300a-10: mu zi ser po zho do //
T16TD4438E:300a-11: shing aa dha dza ri gsum /
T16TD4438E:300a-12: na k'a tsa li tshom pa re /
T16TD4438E:300a-13: tu la pa'i khu ba rnams sgang lkogs nang du blugs /
T16TD4438E:300a-14: 'jim pa sbyin pos kha legs par bcad /
T16TD4438E:300a-15: de nas ras bdun brtsegs par 'jim pa dang bcas gril lugs gong ltar byas la khog ma'i nang du bye ma blugs nas bye ma dang bcas me gtong lugs gong 'dra'i nyin zhag phyed kyi bar btang la grang ba dang bton te sgo nga dal bus bcags pas dngul chu dug bral lhad med du 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:300a-16: yang lugs gcig la dngul chu zho bdun dang pi pi la'i shu na pa nyag gang bcas rdo gzhong du nyin bdun gyi bar du nyed /
T16TD4438E:300a-17: bham ga re'i thang chu blug la slar yang nyin bdun nyed /
T16TD4438E:300a-18: de nas rdza sa'i bar du skam thag legs par chod pa'i nang du li shi zho do dang bcas blug la kha legs par bcad bar du (pi pi ling) 'jim pa blug pa'i ras rim pa gsum gyis dril /
T16TD4438E:300b-0: khog ma bye mas brgyangs @300b par kha bcad de me gtong lugs sogs gong bzhin nyin zhag phrugs gcig gi bar byas te grang ba dang bton pas kyang dug bral lhad med du 'byung /
T16TD4438E:300b-3: gsha' tshe gsum mang nyung ji ltar byed kyang cha bsnyams la khog ma'i nang du blug / de la me btang ste zhu ba dang snod gzhan zhig tu ba mar sar pa btsags legs par bcad /
T16TD4438E:300b-4: de nas lcags skyogs chung ngu zhig gis mar (rangka) nyung zad re blug la (nyi shu kha sarba lha ti tsha yang zer/) dkrug / mar blug pa'i du ba yal ba dang yang mar blugs pa sogs lan bdun gyi bar byas /
T16TD4438E:300b-5: de nas bh'a ta'i lo ma dang dhu ti gnyis cha mnyam zhib par btags pa'i phye ma gsha' dkar sogs mi mngon par 'debs shing dkrugs /
T16TD4438E:300b-6: de nas kha bcad la nyi ma'i bzhi cha tsam gyi bar la me shin tu che ba btang /
T16TD4438E:300b-7: de nas me thag bcad de grang ba dang bton la /
T16TD4438E:300b-8: se ba bzhi nas phyed gsum gyi bar nad babs lci yang dang bstun te btang bas rlung mkhris bad kan gsum ka la phan zhing n'a ga ra sa ste de dang ka ra bsres nas zos na dang sa ma 'dzag pa la mchog tu phan /
T16TD4438E:300b-9: aa ru ra bsnan nas btang na mgo bo na ba la phan no //
T16TD4438E:300b-10: rdza'i bar bu'i nang du zha nye dkar po nyag gang blug / de la me btang nas zhu ba dang dngul chu nyag phyed blugs la me mtshams ma bcad par gtong zhing skya bas dkrug pa dang mnyam dub bla btags pa nyag phyed rim bzhin btab ste gsum ga legs par 'dres pa dang par bu'i kha bcad rlung mi 'chor bar bya /
T16TD4438E:300b-11: de nas ras dang rdzas khrag gang rigs kyis brdzis pa'i 'jim pa byugs shing yang ras dkri ba sogs rim pa sum brtsegs su byas /
T16TD4438E:300b-12: de skams pa dang nyin zhag lnga me mtshams ma chad par btang /
T16TD4438E:300b-13: de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton /
T16TD4438E:301a-0: ba'i zho ras la btsags te khu ba legs par bton pas brdzis pa srab 'thug sor gang tsam yod pa'i sgor mor btang la ras kyis bdun brtsegs @301a * //
T16TD4438E:301a-1: tsam dril nas skud pas bsdams te gci ba'i me'i dkyil du bcug la ras tshig tsam gyi tshod bzhag / de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton la phye mar nyes pa dang zhos khu ba byas nas brdzis te bsreg pa sogs gong ltar lan nyi shu'i bar byas pa ni bangge shva ra zer te stobs bskyed dang /
T16TD4438E:301a-2: nad tsha grang gsar rnying thams cad la phan zhing /
T16TD4438E:301a-3: nad gzhi che ba la gtong na thun tshad sran ma tsam dang /
T16TD4438E:301a-4: gzhi chung ba dang nad med la 'bras nyis 'gyur tsam re gtong ngo //
T16TD4438E:301a-5: 'di'i phan yon bsam gyis mi khyab po ;
T16TD4438E:301a-6: ; zangs mang nyung ci 'dod pa sbrang gshog legs par brdungs /
T16TD4438E:301a-7: rdza snod kyi nang du ba'i gcin la chu cung zad bsres par kha ri lu na dang mnyam du btab la nyin phyed kyi bar du me btang la btsos /
T16TD4438E:301a-8: de nas bton la snod bkrus pa'i nang du slar yang (dambha) aambam li'i 'bru chur btab pa'i nang du nyin phyed 'tshed /
T16TD4438E:301a-9: de nas chu de phol snod bkrus te skyu ru ra chur btab pa'i nang du nyin phyed 'tshed /
T16TD4438E:301a-10: de nas ba'i dar bar kha ri lu na btab pa'i nang du zhag bdun gyi bar du 'jog cing 'di skabs me gtong mi dgos /
T16TD4438E:301a-11: de nas zangs gshog ston la legs par bkrus te mu zi ser po dang cha mnyam bteg pa phye mar byas la rdza'i par bu'i nang du mu zi bting /
T16TD4438E:301a-12: de steng zangs gshog gcig bzhag / yang mu zi bting /
T16TD4438E:301a-13: de steng zangs gshog 'jog pa sogs kyi zangs gshog grangs du yod par brtsegs la kha 'grig par bcad de rlung mi 'chor bar byas /
T16TD4438E:301a-14: de ras gyis gtums shing 'jim pas 'byug pa sogs sum rim tsam byas la slar yang phyi 'jim pas legs par gtums la skam thag chod pa dang /
T16TD4438E:301a-15: de nas sa dong brus par gci ba'i me'i nang du nyin gcig gi bar du bsregs /
T16TD4438E:301a-16: thal ba grang thag chod pa dang bton la rdo gzhong gi nang du nyes nas phye mar byas la thun sran ma bzhi tsam gyi tshod re btang bas grang ba'i rigs dang /
T16TD4438E:301b-1: rked pa na ba rnams la phan /
T16TD4438E:301b-2: yang sho mo sa zho gang phye mar btags pa dang gong gi zangs thal se ba bzhi bsres pa thun re byas btang bas yan lag zha 'khums la mchog tu pan no //
T16TD4438E:301b-3: su ma gser zho do dang sa ba brgyad la sbrang gshog 'than /
T16TD4438E:301b-4: mtshal se ba bco lnga dang bil ba'i nang gi 'bru (mi thi) gnyis zhib par btags par chu cung zad kyang blug pa'i skyo ma gser shog la byugs /
T16TD4438E:301b-5: de nas gser shog sgril la bil ba'i nang du bcug (kho da yon sog gser) kha legs par bcad de ras kyis dril la 'jim bsor phyed tsam byugs /
T16TD4438E:301b-6: skam thag chod pa dang sa dong brus par gci ba'i me nang du nyin gcig bsregs la grang thag chod pa dang bton te phye mar byas la 'bras nyis 'gyur tsam gyi tshad lga ser dang mnyam du zos na glo nad dang dbugs mi bde ba g-yal ba rnams la phan zhing skyug pa chod /
T16TD4438E:301b-7: ba'i gci ba'i thal ba dang mnyam du zos na dang kha dang skom nad la phan /
T16TD4438E:301b-8: lga dang mnyam du btang na skran /
T16TD4438E:301b-11: rlung skran rnams rtsa ba nas 'byin par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:301b-12: lcags phye nyag gang la dngul chu nyag phyed bsres te zhib par nyes /
T16TD4438E:301b-13: chu la shing gi wa kva ra'i khu ba blugs nas gar sla zho tsam byas la /
T16TD4438E:301b-14: rdo gzhong nang du nyi mar nyed cing skams pa dang khu ba gar sla sogs gong ltar byas pa lan brgya dang brgyad kyi bar byed /
T16TD4438E:301b-15: de nas rdza'i par (lu ta) bu'i nang du blug / kha rlung mi 'tshor bar legs par bcad /
T16TD4438E:301b-16: de nas 'jim pa dang ras spel mar lan bdun gyi bar sgril bskam thag chod pa dang rdza'i khog ma che ba mthil du bug pa rgya khab kyi rtse tshud pa tsam yod pa zhig bye mas brdzangs pa'i dkyil du bcug / kha legs par bsgrigs te rlung sogs ye mi 'tshor ba byas te nyin zhag bzhi'i ring me shin tu tsha ba mtshams ma chad pa gtong /
T16TD4438E:301b-17: 'di skabs las byed mi ma gtogs 'grul gcod /
T16TD4438E:301b-18: de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton la thun tshad 'bras tsam re bya /
T16TD4438E:302a-0: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa rims sogs nad gsar @302a * //
T16TD4438E:302a-1: rnying gang dang gang la yang 'dis mi phan pa med pas sman thams cad kyi rgyal po lta bu'o //
T16TD4438E:302a-2: zha nye nag po nyag phyed lcags snod kyi nang du bzhu /
T16TD4438E:302a-3: sa ser zhib par btags pa'i nang du blug / yang bton la bzhu ba sogs lan nyer gcig gi bar byed /
T16TD4438E:302a-4: ldong ros dang tsha la nyag re bsres la zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:302a-5: rdza snod du zha nye blug la me btang ste zhu ba dang gong gi tsha la ldong ros bsres pa'i phye ma cung zad re 'debs pa dang mnyam du skya bas dkrugs /
T16TD4438E:302a-6: legs par 'dres nas thal bar song ba dang shing gi wa na (ma si la) kra ra'i khu (so h'a [?]) ba blug ste skya bas dkrug cing nyin phyed kyi bar me btang /
T16TD4438E:302a-7: thal bar song ba dang kha legs par bcad la nyin mtshan lnga dang nyi ma'i bzhi cha gcig gi bar me btang /
T16TD4438E:302a-8: de nas grang ba dang bton la thun tshad sran ma nyis 'gyur tsam sbrang rtsi dang mnyam du btang na rlung gi nad gsar rnying thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:302a-9: ka ra dang mnyam du btang na khrag gi rigs la phan /
T16TD4438E:302a-10: lga dang mnyam du btang na bad kan gyi rigs dang ma 'ju ba sogs pho ba'i nad la phan /
T16TD4438E:302a-11: aa ru ra'i phye ma dang mnyam du btang na mkhris pa'i rigs la phan /
T16TD4438E:302a-12: pi pi ling dang mnyam du btang na dang kha 'byed /
T16TD4438E:302a-13: khrag dang rlung la brten nas dangs ma 'dzag na bu ram rnying pa dang mnyam du btang /
T16TD4438E:302a-14: mkhris pa la brten nas 'dzag na aa ngu ra dang mnyam du btang /
T16TD4438E:302a-15: ba mar gsar pa dang mnyam du zos na stobs skyed par byed /
T16TD4438E:302a-16: gcong gis zin pa'i nad lus shin tu rid na gur gum dang mnyam du gtong zhing gzhan yang nad tshod dang bstun te kha bsgyur byas te btang bas kun la phan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:302a-17: ti tsha'am gsha' tshe nya ga gang rdza snod du bzhu la pa ra ki ri nyag phyed dang /
T16TD4438E:302a-18: so ra nyag phyed bsres te zhib par btags pa'i phye ma cung zad re 'debs /
T16TD4438E:302a-19: shing lcags kyi gzar bu chung ngu'i ltag pas nyed cing dkrug nyin phyed kyi bar byas pas 'dres te thal bar so nga ba dang khed sa rgyab la nye ma'i bzhi cha gcig me btang /
T16TD4438E:302a-20: grang thag chod pa dang bton la (ze tsha) phye mar byas te dar la btsags /
T16TD4438E:302b-0: de nas phye ma de @302b dang /
T16TD4438E:302b-1: li shi / dz'a ti gsum se ba re /
T16TD4438E:302b-4: pi pi ling gsum se ba gsum re rnams zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:302b-5: sbrang rtsis rta byas la ril bu sran mnyis 'gyur tsam sgril la ril bu re btang bas byis pa 'khru ba'i nad dang 'cham pa la phan zhing gnyid ma khug par btang bas kyang (la wam ga) gnyid (dza yi pla [?]) du 'gro //
T16TD4438E:302b-6: aa (mari [?] tse shunthi bi pa wi) rur dang bsres nas btang na dbugs mi bde ba la phan /
T16TD4438E:302b-7: mgo bo na na ril bu chur brdar la sna bug tu blug pas phan par 'gyur /
T16TD4438E:302b-8: ga bur dang bsres nas btang na kha'i dri ngan pa rtsa ba nas 'byin /
T16TD4438E:302b-9: zho dang mnyam du btang na skran thon /
T16TD4438E:302b-10: kha ru tsha dang mnyam du btang na ma 'ju ba'i nad sel lo //
T16TD4438E:302b-11: zangs mang nyung gar byed kyang sbrang gshog legs par 'then la jem rtsis chung ngur gtubs pa dang mu zi ser po zangs che chung gang yin gyi phyed mar gtang ba dam pe'i khog par blug la skyu ru ra dang nem bu'i chu blug la kha legs par bcad de nas kyi dkyil du zla ba gcig bzhag / de nas bton la phye mar byas te thun tshad se ba bzhi'i rtsis chu grang gis 'phul la btang na dug dang mkhris pa'i nad 'phral du skyugs nas phan zhing srin nad la btang na yang 'khru skyug yong la /
T16TD4438E:302b-12: gzhan yang skyugs kyis phan pa'i nad gang la 'ang btang bas skyug sman gyi mchog go / kha parsa dha nyag phyed pa rdar ba'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4438E:302b-13: mu zi ser po nyag phyed /
T16TD4438E:302b-14: dngul chu spor gang gsum rdo gzhong du nyi ma'i bzhi cha gcig gi ring zhib par nyes la gi wa kva ra'i khu bas gar sla zho tsam byas pa nyi ma dang grib ma phyed khyer du nyes /
T16TD4438E:302b-15: skam thag chod pa dang slar yang khu ba lugs (ti tsha'am gsha' tshe/) pa sogs nyin bcu gsum gyi bar byed /
T16TD4438E:302b-16: bzhu shel gyi dam per ras dang 'jim pa spel mar byugs pa bdun brtsegs byas pa skam thag chod pa dang blug la kha rdzas sbyin po mgar ba'i so rdog / aar ka / bu ram /
T16TD4438E:303a-0: rgya gar stod ja rnams cha mnyam pa zhib par btags pa ba'i 'o mas brdzis la 'dam btags nyin gcig byas pa'i 'jim pas dam pe'i kha shin tu dam par bkag / de ras kyis gtums la gong gi 'jim pas dam pe yongs @303a * //
T16TD4438E:303a-1: rdzogs la 'byug / de skam pa dang khog ma che ba zhig gi nang phye ma'i dkyil du bcug la kha legs par bcad de nyin zhag bzhi'i bar me mtshams ma chad par btang /
T16TD4438E:303a-2: de nas grang ba dang bton la nad babs che na sran ma gcig tsam nas nad med la 'bras nyis 'gyur gyi bar 'os 'gab btang bas nad ngos zin ma zin gsar rnying gang la yang phan zhing /
T16TD4438E:303a-3: nad med kyis zos na rgas kha sra ba dang stobs bskyed pa la sogs pa phan yon bsam mi khyab bo //
T16TD4438E:303a-4: zha nye dkar po nyag gang lugs kong du bzhu la legs par bzhu ba dang snum gyi dkyil du blug / de 'khang ba dang yang bzhu blug gong ltar lan gsum gyi bar du byed /
T16TD4438E:303a-5: de nas snod che ba zhig tu bzhu la 'bras bu gsum zhib par btags pa'i bye ma thal 'debs pa ltar rim bzhin btabs nas thal bar ma song bar lcags skyogs chung ngu'i ltag pas nyed /
T16TD4438E:303a-6: de nas kha legs par bcad la nyi ma'i brgyad cha tsam gyi bar me btang /
T16TD4438E:303a-7: grang thag chod pa dang bton la zho ras la btsags te khu ba legs par bton pas brdzis te srab mthug sor gang tsam yod pa'i sgor mor btang /
T16TD4438E:303a-8: de ras kyis bdun brtsegs tsam dril la skud pas bsdoms /
T16TD4438E:303a-9: gci ba'i me'i dkyil du bcug la ras tshig tsam gyi tshad bzhag / de nas me shi zhing grang thag chod pa dang bton la zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:303a-11: gsha' dkar srab mthu ga shog bu tsam brdungs la /
T16TD4438E:303a-12: bod kyi so ma ra tsa'i lo ma zhib par 'phur ba /
T16TD4438E:303a-13: ras kha gang las phad bu bzos pa'i nang du so ma ra tsa bting la /
T16TD4438E:303a-14: gsha' dkar sbrang gshog de'i steng du rim brtsegs su bzhag pa'i bar mtshams su so ma ra tsa sor gsum yod pa byas la kha btsems te /

T16TD4438E:316b-6: ba dkar rkyang nag rkyang lta bu spu mdog gang yin kyang mdog gzhan ma 'dres pa'i kha gtsang gi mar btsags bcad pa'i nang du btab ste 'khang pa dang bud med dus bab kyi zla mtshan 'dzag nas tshad pa'i nyin khong du btang na bud med phru gu mi yong ba'ang nges par sbrum par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:316b-11: n'a ga ge sar rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags pa dar la btsags pa thur mgo gsum ba mdog gcig gi 'o ma khyor gang tsam la btab ste dus gong mtshungs la byin na'ang nges par mngal dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:316b-12: ma la chags kyang mi gnas par 'jig na /
T16TD4438E:316b-13: l'a la ka ma la'i rtsa ba ba'i 'o mar btsos /
T16TD4438E:316b-14: de nas slar yang ba mar gyi nang du btsos la zhib par btags la gong gi ba mar bzhu ba dang mnyam du btang na 'jig par mi 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:316b-15: yang bilba'i 'bru dang smyug ma'i lo ma cha mnyam zhib par btags la chus rta byas nas nyin bdun gyi bar btang kyang mi 'jig go //
T16TD4438E:316b-16: mig sman gyi (zhag bdun nad kyang grag 'ong) sbyor thabs ni /
T16TD4438E:316b-19: sa mu dra pha la rgya mtsho (sa mu dra phen) lbu ba /
T16TD4438E:316b-20: mu tig / byi dang ga bsdu ba sha pa ri ya /
T16TD4438E:316b-24: pho ris rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags dar la legs par btsags /
T16TD4438E:317a-0: @317a * // 'khar snod du tsan dan dmar po'i skya ba'i mjug zangs dmar gyis gtums pas nyin phyed tsam skam nyed bya /
T16TD4438E:317a-1: de nas bcus nas zhag gcig song ba'i chu cung zad blugs la nyi ma'i bzhi cha gcig tsam bsnur la ril bur dril /
T16TD4438E:317a-2: skam pa dang rdo 'jam po'i ngos su chu dang lhan du brdar nas mig la byugs na ling tog / steng 'og gi 'gribs /
T16TD4438E:317a-5: rgyang mig mi gsal ba sogs mig gi nad mtha' dag la phan no //
T16TD4438E:317a-6: ki ka ra'i me tog / rgya gar stod ja /
T16TD4438E:317a-9: pa ta ki ri rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags pa dar la btsags /
T16TD4438E:317a-10: ra'i 'o mas khu ba phyas la ril bu sgril ba zhos khub byas brdar nas mig steng 'og gang rigs kyis bsgribs nas mi mthong bar byugs na mthong bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:317a-11: ri phyugs kyi gci ba ser kha ma me la bsregs pa'i thal ba zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:317a-12: der chur blugs la ras sam dar la tshags thengs gnyis byas /
T16TD4438E:317a-13: de nas chu de dangs su bcug la dal bus pho bas mthil du chags pa'i thal ba de skams pa dang /
T16TD4438E:317a-14: 'khar snod du pang kha'i snum [?] dang lhan du tsan dan gyi skya ba zangs gtums can gyis nyi ma gsum gyi bar bsnur ba chung ngu re mig la byugs na sha 'dzer dang /
T16TD4438E:317a-15: dmar por song ba sogs khrag la brten pa'i mig nad thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:317a-16: bdud rtsi mig sman gyi sbyor ba ni /
T16TD4438E:317a-21: pa ti ka ti hirma dzi /
T16TD4438E:317a-26: ba ru ra'i 'bru'i nang gi sting po /
T16TD4438E:317a-27: sha pa ri ya rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags pa dar la btsags /
T16TD4438E:317b-0: rdo gzhong shin tu 'jam po'i nang du (son makshi) chu bcus nas zhag gcig song ba sa gar sla zho tsam sbrus pa skam thag mchod par nyed thengs gcig / de nas nyi mar cung zad cig bzhag / yang bud med bu skyes pa'i 'o mas gar sla gong tsam byas pa ma skam par nyed thengs gcig / de bzhin du ba'i 'o mas thengs @317b gcig / ra'i 'o mas thongs gcig sprus pa'i ma skam tsam la ril bu sgril la skam thag chod pa dang sbrang rtsis rta byas brdar nas mig la byugs na rlung la brten pa'i mig nad thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:317b-1: ra'i 'o mas khu ba byas nas byugs na srod long la phan /
T16TD4438E:317b-2: bud med kyi 'o mas khu ba byas nas byugs na khrag rlung la brten pa'i mig nad thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:317b-3: pa'i gcin gyis khu ba byas nas byugs na mig tsha zhing mig rnag mang du 'dzag pa la phan /
T16TD4438E:317b-4: 'u su'i khu bas rta byas byugs na sha 'dzer dang mig dmar por song ba la phan no //
T16TD4438E:317b-5: de rnams ni bdud rtsi mig sman gyi sbyor ba kha bsgyur dang bcas pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4438E:317b-8: ra tan dze ti skyur ba gnyis cha mnyam zhib par btags 'o mar sbyar te byugs na rgyang mig mi gsal ba la phan //
T16TD4438E:317b-9: du ba ral pa zho gang /
T16TD4438E:317b-12: dan rog brgya tham pa lce ston /
T16TD4438E:317b-14: danda drug cu tham pa rnams (ka yi pa la zer) zhib par btags nimbu 'i khu bas 'dam btags byas la ril bu dril te pad kha tsam re chu la sbyar nas byugs na 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:317b-15: sha za yi dags la sogs pa gnod pas mig na ba la phan no //
T16TD4438E:317b-16: 'khar snod du nimbu'i chur sma ru mgo nag dkar po zhib par brdar te steng glang po che'i rmig pa nyis 'gyur gyis mang ba zhig tu brdar /
T16TD4438E:317b-17: de steng ku kum sma ru mgo nag gi gsum cha gnyis tsam brdar /
T16TD4438E:317b-18: de rnams legs par 'dres pa dang mig la nyin gsum nas bdun gyi bar gang rigs 'byug cing sman zhag gang 'byug gi ring phyir mi 'dod /
T16TD4438E:317b-19: khyad par rlung gi rigs ma phog pa byas pas ling tog / rva /
T16TD4438E:317b-21: 'gri bas sogs mig nad mtha' dag la mchog tu phan no //
T16TD4438E:317b-24: yung ba chung ngu bcas brdar la mi'i 'o mas khu ba byas nas mig la byugs na khrag gis mig dmar por song ba dang sha 'dzer la phan /
T16TD4438E:318a-1: ser po dang gla rtsi sbyar la byugs na tsha 'khrug mig chu 'dzag ste za phrug byed pa rnams la phan /
T16TD4438E:318a-4: si ra sa'i 'bru rnams se ba bzhi re'i rtses zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:318a-5: ba gsar pa'i chu bre gsum lcags snod nang du skya ba'i mgo zangs kyis gtu mas pas dkrugs pa dang me btang la chu phyed tsam skams pa dang /
T16TD4438E:318a-6: gong gi sman btab ste skyo ma gar phyogs tsam byas slar 'byug skabs ba'i chus klad la byugs na bar 'grib chu 'dzag pa za 'phrug / rdzi ma mig la zug pa sogs mig gi nad thams cad la phan no //
T16TD4438E:318a-7: ka ye pha la zhib mor btags pa chur sbyar te byugs na srod long la phan no //
T16TD4438E:318a-8: rva ling shin tu che bas khebs shing na na nimbu'i khu bar rgya tshva yungs 'bru tsam re brdar nas ra ling gi thog tu nyin gsum gyi bar blugs pas 'phral bu zug gzer cung zad 'byung yang myur du phan par 'gyur ro /
T16TD4438E:318a-9: (/'o ma thang gis) yang mig la rva ling gis cher na na bzhu shel snying po pho ris tsam re zhib par btags la chur sbyar nas nyin gsum gyi bar blugs na nyin dang por zug gzer cung zad ldang /
T16TD4438E:318a-10: gnyis par mig skrangs po shin tu che zhing zug gzer kyang 'byung /
T16TD4438E:318a-11: nyin gsum par zug gzer skrangs po zhi ba dang (kadzdza) mnyam du rva ling gang yang med par 'gyur zhing 'og 'grib kyis mi mthong ba yang gsal bar byed do //
T16TD4438E:318a-12: mig gangs phyid kyis na ba'i zug gzer che na chu grang gtsang ma snod gang yang rung bar blugs la mig ma btsums par gdong chu'i nang du bcug la zug gzer ma chag par bdugs pas myur du phan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:318a-13: de bzhin yan lag kha bas phyid pa yang chu grang mo'i nang du bdugs pas phan no //
T16TD4438E:318b-0: phat ki ri rnams cha mnyam ste ni mba'i khu ba byung na rab de min chur sbyangs nas mig gi phyi nang la byugs pas mig 'bras chen por song zhing mig sprin dmar ba nyin @318b mtshan gnyis kar nad zug shin tu che ba la phan /
T16TD4438E:318b-1: ka ni ya ra'i rtsa ba /
T16TD4438E:318b-6: pi pi ling gi rtsa ba /
T16TD4438E:318b-8: lga bzang po rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags /
T16TD4438E:318b-9: lga bzang ba chur spangs pas khu ba byas nas ril bu sran ma tsam dril la btang bas khrag la brten pa'i tshigs na ba thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:318b-11: lcang nag gi rtsa ba dang lo ma /
T16TD4438E:318b-12: skyi pa'i rtsa ba sdong po lo ma 'bras bu /
T16TD4438E:318b-13: gze ma rnams cha mnyam la 'om bu dang lcang nag gi rtsa ba cung zad mang ba bcas gzhogs la khog ma che ba mthil du bug pa nas shong ba tsam yod pa zhig gi nang du blugs /
T16TD4438E:318b-14: (dzha yu) khebs (madzha na) gcod rgyab la (myu ba) rlangs pa mi 'chor ba kha legs (go sha ru) bar bcad de mtshams rdza sa'i 'ji ma pas gtums ras kyis dril yang 'jim pa 'byug pa dang ras kyis dril ba sogs lnga brtsigs tsam byas /
T16TD4438E:318b-15: sa dong brus pa khog ma cung zad chung ba zhig bcug la sas stems /
T16TD4438E:318b-16: de'i khar gong gi khog ma bzhag / khog ma gnyis kyi mtshams legs par bsgrigs la 'jim pas rlung mi 'chor bar byas /
T16TD4438E:318b-17: de nas khog ma che ba shing dang gci ba'i dkyil du bcug la nyi ma'i bzhi cha tsam zhig me shin tu tsha ba btang /
T16TD4438E:318b-18: de nas grang thag chod pa dang bton pas khog ma chung bar gsham du chu dang khar snum spris ma ltar chags yod pa de bton la thur mgo re tsam lga dang mnyam du btang na bse dug min pa'i rlung la brten pa'i nad tsha grang thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:318b-19: li shi dang mnyam du btang na grang ba la brten pa'i nad thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:318b-20: yung ba dang mnyam du btang na khrag la brten pa'i nad gsar rnying thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:318b-21: rtsam pa'i pag dang mnyam du btang na bad kan gyi rigs thams cad la phan /
T16TD4438E:319a-0: gzhan 'dres med pa'i mkhris pa rkyang pa'i nad dang 'grim pa gnyis por ba'i gzhan ma nad gang la yang mi 'grib med cing khyad par yan lag zha ba @319a * //
T16TD4438E:319a-1: skams pa rnams la khong du btang zhing snum byugs pas nad med lta bur sos par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:319a-6: rnga mong rnams kyi brun gang legs par byas pa'i skam po khog ma steng shod du ldugs lugs sogs gong ltar byas pas snum bton la aa kar kar /
T16TD4438E:319a-8: pi pi ling gi rtsa ba /
T16TD4438E:319a-9: (ka bu rar surki) pi pi ling /
T16TD4438E:319a-10: (tsi ri shag au tam) la la phud chung ba /
T16TD4438E:319a-11: so ma ra tsa rnams cha mnyam zhi ba bar btags pa dar la btsags /
T16TD4438E:319a-12: de thams cad dang cha mnyam pa'i snum blugs la ril bu skyu ru ra tsam dril la btang na /
T16TD4438E:319a-16: chu ser rnams la phan zhing lus stobs rgyas pa dang khu ba 'phel bas 'dod pa spyod nus pa /
T16TD4438E:319a-17: dang kha 'byed pa sogs la phan no //
T16TD4438E:319a-18: ri phyugs lo gcig tsam 'gro ba'i lci ba /
T16TD4438E:319a-19: ra'i ril ma gnyis skam thag bcad cing gang legs par byas /
T16TD4438E:319a-20: khog ma steng shod du me gtong lugs sogs gong ltar byas pas snum 'byung ba sbrang rtsi dang yung ba gang rung dang mnyam du khong du btang zhing snum rgyang pas phyi ma bsku mnye byas pas chu pags 'grams /
T16TD4438E:319a-21: za phrug / tshags tshigs na ba sogs chu ser gyi nad thams cad la mchog tu phan zhing mig la byugs kyang rlung chu ser la brten pa'i mig nad la phan no //
T16TD4438E:319a-22: gro dang skyer pa mang nyung mnyam pa dang /
T16TD4438E:319a-23: shu dag de'i sum cha tsam bcas pas snod du blugs la snum 'don lugs gong ltar byas pa se ba bzhi tsam re khong du btang na'ang nad tsha grang gsar rnying kun la phan pa'i spyi 'joms so //
T16TD4438E:319a-26: (da ru ha lad) pha ta ki di rnams cha mnyam bzhu shel gyi dam pe 'jim pa dang ras bsnol mar lnga brtsegs byugs pa zhig gi nang du phyed tsam gong ba blugs /
T16TD4438E:319b-0: rdza snod che ba zhig gi phyed tsam gci ba'i mes @319b bkang ba'i nang du gong gi dam pe gyen bsregs nyal stabs su bzhag / khardza snod kyi phyir 'ong ba byas la steng du'ang me btang /
T16TD4438E:319b-1: khog ma de rdo'i sgyeng pu gsum sgram lta bur bzhag pa'i mthil nas kyang me cung zad gtong /
T16TD4438E:319b-2: khog ma'i phyir bzhu shel gyi dam pe gcig bzhag la dam pe gnyis kyi kha sprad pa'i mtshams la lhang tsher bkab la phyir 'jim pa byugs te rlung mi 'chor ba byas /
T16TD4438E:319b-3: me nyi ma'i brgyad cha tsam zhig btang bas /
T16TD4438E:319b-4: dam pe phyi ma'i nang du snum 'ong ba de thigs pa gsum tsam re dang ;
T16TD4438E:319b-5: la la phud seb bzhi tsam zhib par btags pa dang mnyam du btang bas nad tsha grang gsar rnying thams cad la ni mi phan pa med do //
T16TD4438E:319b-9: su ma la dkar po dang ser po //
T16TD4438E:319b-11: mtshal cog la ma rnams cha mnyam btags pa bzhu shel gyi dam per blugs la snum 'don lugs gong mtshungs byas pa'i snum de mdze'i rma'am /
T16TD4438E:319b-13: phol mig sogs la byugs na phan no //
T16TD4438E:319b-18: aa ru bsregs pa rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags pa dar la btsags /
T16TD4438E:319b-19: lga spangs pa'i chus sbrus la ril bu skyu ru ra tsam sgril ba ril bu re btang na glo dang mgo bo na ba la phan zhing dang kha 'byed do //
T16TD4438E:319b-20: ma ru rtse'i 'bras bu zhib par btags (ba la sha) la chu grang gis rta byas btang na glo ba'i rnag thon par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:319b-21: spyi bzhur brdungs pa'i khu ba khong du btang na phyi nang gi rtsa 'phyus pa'i rigs la phan no //
T16TD4438E:319b-22: tha ram brdungs pa'i 'byar khyis rmugs pa'i rma la dkris na phan /
T16TD4438E:319b-23: lung kha ri (lpa tsha yin/) zhes pa'i sman tshad par phan /
T16TD4438E:319b-25: shing sha sogs sha mo'i rigs gang rnyed bye kar dang mnyam du sbyar ba'i thang khong du btang na mkhal nad gzer zug 'phral du gcog /
T16TD4438E:320a-0: @320a * // mkhan pa brdungs pa'i khu bar pho ris zhib par btags la btab ste khong du btang na khog pa'i srin nad kun la phan /
T16TD4438E:320a-1: mkhan pa'i dugs byas na pho long 'khrog pa myur du zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:320a-2: spa yag pas skrangs po dang rma la phan /
T16TD4438E:320a-4: (na ru ba) tsi ta cha bdun /
T16TD4438E:320a-5: aa ru ra cha drug rnams zhib par btags la chu skol gyis rta byas btang na ma 'ju ba /
T16TD4438E:320a-7: glang thabs rnams la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320a-8: ba dmar ma dang bu ram sbyar ba chus 'bul la btang na sha ser dang mig ser la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320a-9: ba dmar lga ser gyis khu ba byas la steng grib gyi nad mgor thebs na rna bar blug cing lus gzhan la thebs na khong du btang bas gza'i rigs mtha' (tsi tu wa tu tam zhing chu la sogs la yod pa'i srog chags dmar po chung ngu zhig yod/) dag la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320a-11: r'a hu'i dug 'phog pa yin na lo phyed gsum /
T16TD4438E:320a-12: spen pa'i dug phog na lo lnga /
T16TD4438E:320a-13: ke tu'i dug phog na brgyad de de bsgral nas gza'i nad kyis 'tsho 'chi gang byed las mi gnas so //
T16TD4438E:320a-14: rgya khur dang bye kar dang cha mnyam sbyar ba khong du btang bas mi phyugs gang gi yang chu 'gags pa sel lo //
T16TD4438E:320a-15: aa ru ra gnyis sprel mgo gzhogs phyed na ba la gang na phyogs su bsdams pas phan zhing sna khrag kyang chod la ya ma'i 'bus na ba sel lo //
T16TD4438E:320a-17: (dhu ri) btsag zhib par btags khong du'ang cung zad btang zhing gang na sar byugs pas me lce 'khor lo la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320a-18: tsan dan su ra zhib par btags la chu skol gyis 'phul nas btang na khrag la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320a-19: tsha la bsregs pa'i thal pa /
T16TD4438E:320a-21: kha ru tsha rnams zhib par btags la thun tshad thur mgo do tsam re btang na pho bar na zug byed pa rlung dang ma 'ju ba'i rigs kun la phan zhing dang kha 'byed do //
T16TD4438E:320a-23: kha ru tsha cha gcig / tsi tra cha gsum /
T16TD4438E:320b-0: @320b lga dkar po cha drug / aa ru ra cha drug rnams zhib par btags dar la btsags te /
T16TD4438E:320b-1: thun tshad gong bzhin btang bas ldan 'dus kyi nad gdong ser po dang dmar por song ba mig mi gsal shed chung ba'i mgo bo 'khor ba rnams la phan no //
T16TD4438E:320b-2: aa ru ra mer bsregs pa'i thal ba /
T16TD4438E:320b-6: aa ru nag chung rnams zhib par btags la lga'i khu bas ril bu skyu ru ra tsam byas la gong du btang na glo nad kun dang pho bar rlung zhugs pa khrag skran rus tshad /
T16TD4438E:320b-7: dang kha (phyed cha tsam) 'gags pa rnams la phan /
T16TD4438E:320b-8: phag brun bsregs pa'i thal ba bong bu'i gcin gyis khu ba byas nas sna la blugs pas ya ma klad gzer la phan /
T16TD4438E:320b-9: ka ranydza ba'i 'o mar btab pa'i khu ba khong du btang bas khog srin dang gzhang srin gyi nad la phan ;
T16TD4438E:320b-10: sha 'bras dang bye kar cha bsnyams pa zhib par btags la zho dang sbyar nas btang na tshad 'khru chod par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:320b-11: 'gron bu bsregs pa'i thal ba mi'i 'o mar sbyar la rna bar blugs na rnag 'dzag pa chod do //
T16TD4438E:320b-12: dza mu ni zhib par btags pa chu la sbyar nas byugs na grang thor rgyab pa la phan /
T16TD4438E:320b-13: skyu ru ra aa rag gi nang du sbangs pa'i khu ba byugs na skra tshan che bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:320b-14: phur mong nag po sha'i srubs rnams la rdzongs na 'a [?] bu mi 'byung zhing shing kun dri mas kyang thub po //
T16TD4438E:320b-17: kha ru tsha gsum cha mnyam zhib par btags la chu skol gyis rta byas btang na pho ba dang rked pa na bar phan /
T16TD4438E:320b-19: pho ris cha gcig / tshva cha phyed rnams zhib par btags pa chur sbyar te byugs na so rtsa dam zhing brtan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:320b-20: la la phud mer bsregs pa'i du ba kha la btang na so srin na ba la phan /
T16TD4438E:320b-21: ba ta ki ti (hong len) ai'i 'bru'i du ba 'then pas so srin la phan /
T16TD4438E:321a-0: rgun (da'i kha) 'brum dkar po mkhris pa dang @321a * //
T16TD4438E:321a-2: ma nu khrag can gyi nang gi khrag rkang lag gi ser kar byugs kyang phan zhing spos dkar gyi phye ma btab kyang phan no //
T16TD4438E:321a-5: lga gsum cha mnyam sbrang rtsir sbyar ba btang na khrag 'grim pa'i rigs chod do //
T16TD4438E:321a-10: btsan dug / mu zi ser po rnams cha mnyam /
T16TD4438E:321a-11: po ris nyis 'gyur bcas zhag brgyad tsam gyi bar zhib par btags la 'bras tsam re rgyun du bsten na lus stobs rgyas /
T16TD4438E:321a-21: aa ru ra rnams zhib par btags te ba mar dang sbyar nas skyu ru ra tsam re khong du btang na rlung khrag bad kan sogs 'dus pa'i nad kyis pho long gi yul zug gzer che ba rnams 'joms shing phan la sman bsten ring la 'o ma /
T16TD4438E:321a-22: 'bras pag thu ga rnams las gzhan mi za'o //
T16TD4438E:321a-23: ka ma la do da'i dkyil gyi ljang gu de bzhi lnga re nyin ltar gyis zos na bad rlung mgo 'khor dang mig mi gsal ba la phan no //
T16TD4438E:321a-27: zi ra dkar po rnams cha mnyam phye mar byas pa lugs (che chung ril ma las che tsam mdog smug snum phreng ba byed pa de yin/) kong nang du blug ste kha dam par bcad la rlung mi 'chor bar byas /

T16TD4438E:331b-12: bud med sbrum ma btsa' ma thub pa dang bu ro ma thon par sbrul gyi klad pa mo mtshan gyi nang du byugs na myur du thon par 'gyur ro //

T16TD4438E:331b-16: gos dar bsregs pa'i thal ba snar btab kyang nus pa gong dang 'dra /

T16TD4438E:332a-0: yang chu bal dang shing kun mnyam du btags la chur sbyar ba'i skyo ma @332a * //
T16TD4438E:332a-1: mer bsros pa'i dron mo so gang na sar byugs na phral du phan par 'gyur ro //

T16TD4438E:332a-4: rkang rnams cha mnyam zhib par btags pa cha gcig / shing kun dang snum cha bzhi bsres pa lte bar byugs na sbos khrog rlung gi rigs mtha' dag la phan /

T16TD4438E:332a-10: sbrang dang sbyar na mchi ma 'dzag pa la phan /
T16TD4438E:332a-11: til snum dang sbyar na mig gi za phrug la phan /
T16TD4438E:332a-12: chu dang sbyar na mig gi mthong snang skar ma 'dra ba la phan no //
T16TD4438E:332a-13: zho'i chu dang sbyar na srod long la phan /
T16TD4438E:332a-14: zha nye'i brag zhun mdog dkar ba 'o ma 'dra ba mchog / gzhan brag zhun gyi rigs gang byung yang de'i khu bas yan lag la sogs mtha' dag la phan no //
T16TD4438E:332a-17: mudta sang gti lo phat ki zho re /

T16TD4438E:332a-20: grang 'thag mig la bdugs pas tsha ba dang /

T16TD4438E:332a-32: / shi la dza dhu gdus pa thang du btang //

T16TD4438E:332b-2: bu dang sha ma phral du thon par nges /
T16TD4438E:332b-3: ` / bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //

T16TD4438E:332b-6: khyim pa'ang brtag rung ba ste /

T16TD4438E:332b-8: srod 'khor tsam la dri chu lan gcig dor /

T16TD4438E:332b-10: gsang gnas kyi kha nas dri chu g-yas ngos su 'khyogs nas 'gro na de'i nyin bkra shis shing bde legs dang ldan la bya ba gang brtsams kyang 'grub pa sogs shin tu legs so //
T16TD4438E:332b-11: gzhogs g-yon du 'gro na 'thab mo dang rtsod pa dang 'phrog bcom sogs 'byung zhing bya ba brtsams kyang mi 'grub la /
T16TD4438E:332b-12: gtam mi snyan pa thos pa sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:332b-13: chu bying thad kar 'gro zhing gsang gnas kyi mtshams nas 'og tu thigs pa babs na zas gos sogs yid dang mthun pa'i nor zhig nges par rnyed par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:332b-14: gsang gnas kyi mtshams nas chu rkang gcig la de nas gnyis su gyes shing slar gcig tu 'dril nas 'gro na nye du mdza' bshes sogs yid dang mthun pa'i mi phyogs su song ba zhig nges par 'khor zhing 'phrad par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4438E:332b-15: thog mar 'dril zhing de nas leb mo srab por 'gro la slar yang 'dril nas 'gro na rgyal po'i chad pa'am rku jag stor ba sogs nor la god kha 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:332b-16: chu bying lbu ba dang bcas nas 'gro zhing 'og tu thigs pa yang 'bab la sar babs pa rnams kyang 'khor zhing lbu ba dang bcas na char chen po 'byung ngo //

T16TD4438E:333a-0: chu phar mi 'gro ba gyen du tshur log nas gsang gnas kyi steng du 'bab na zhag @333a * //

T16TD4438E:333a-6: tshes bco lnga'i mi khyi'i skad sogs sems can mi gnas pa'i rkyen med pa'i gnas dben par nam mkha' sprin dang khug rdul sogs kyi grib ma med pa'i shin tu dangs pa'i skabs brtag ste /
T16TD4438E:333a-7: lus gcer bur phyung la lus drong por bsrangs te langs lag pa gnyis cha mnyam du brkyangs /
T16TD4438E:333a-8: zla ba rgyab tu khur te brtags la /
T16TD4438E:333a-9: de yang thog mar sa la shar ba'i grib ma'i mthe bong nas rim bzhin gyen du 'dzegs te mig dang thad mnyam gyen phyogs kyi nam mkha' la grib ma sprin lta bu zhig 'char la /
T16TD4438E:333a-10: de yang nam mkha' 'char ba'i grib ma der lus kyi dbyibs med par zla ba nya lta bu'i bzo dbyibs la shin tu dkar ba zhig snang na tshe ring nad med sdug bsngal mi 'byung /
T16TD4438E:333a-11: bsod nams dang longs spyod mnga' thang rgyas /
T16TD4438E:333a-12: grags pas sa steng khyab pa sogs shin tu legs so //

T16TD4438E:333a-17: lag pha gnyis mi gsal na rang la yang nad 'byung zhing spun zla gcig nges par 'chi'o //
T16TD4438E:333a-18: kha dog nag por snang na nor la god kha chen po 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:333a-19: brla g-yas g-yon gang rigs la bug pa 'dug na chung ma nges par 'chi'o //
T16TD4438E:333b-0: @333b lte ba'i thad du bug pa 'dug na 'thab mo dang kha mchu rtsod pa sogs 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:333b-1: grib ma shin tu ring zhing mgrin pa mi mthong na /
T16TD4438E:333b-2: yul gyi rgyal po sogs mi chen po zhig 'chi bar 'gyur ro //

T16TD4438E:333b-5: ser por mthong na gzhan gyi mi kha 'bab po //

T16TD4438E:333b-7: mig mi mthong na yid dang mthun pa'i mdza' grogs 'chi ba'am nor stor ba sogs kyis sems la sdug bsngal 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:333b-8: lus kyi cha shas thams cad tshang zhing gsal la kha dog dkar zhing bkrag dang ldan na lo drug tshun chad du 'chi pa'i 'jigs pa med cing nad drag po mi 'byung ngo //
T16TD4438E:333b-9: longs spyod dang snyan grags 'phel zhing bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ba 'di yang dag pa'o //

T16TD4438E:333b-13: tsan dan gser las rin che ba //

T16TD4438E:334a-9: bal po yam bu'i rgyal blon la rogs dan dgos tshul gyi sde pa'i hung rgya'i mtshams sbyor song ba la brten sman gyi rigs rnam grangs shin tu mang ba dang bcas me mo sprul lo'i dbyar 'byor pa'i rgya bal gyi slob dpon mkhas pa rnams kyi zhal gyi bdud rtsi las 'ongs pa'i tshe'i rigs byed kyi man ngag gnad kyi snying po bsdus pa 'di nyid mi chos gnad phreng las /

T16TD4438E:334a-21: chu gter slar yang ma bsrubs sngon med pa'i //
